About Us - Gapan City Nueva Ecija
results.p: Gapan was founded in 1595 making it the oldest town in Nueva Ecija and one of the oldest in the Philippines.
Gapan is a component city in the landlocked province of Nueva Ecija. The city has a land area of 164.44 square kilometers or 63.49 square miles.
Barangays in the City of Gapan ; Bayanihan, 0304908001, 034908001, Urban, 5,504 ; Bulak, 0304908002, 034908002, Rural, 2,588.
Gapan, officially the City of Gapan, is a 4th class component city in the province of Nueva Ecija, Philippines.

results.t: Gapan City, Nueva Ecija, Philippines Deforestation Rates ...
results.p: From 2001 to 2023, Gapan City lost 166 ha of tree cover, equivalent to a 11% decrease in tree cover since 2000, and 71.2 kt of CO₂e emissions.
